Command: lite (arg)
         Set custom colors for tells, emotes and channels.

Examples: lite
          lite reset
          lite tell red
          lite emote blue
          lite channel mud green
          lite default tell
          lite default mud

Available colours:
blue, light_blue, red, light_red, cyan, light_cyan,
magenta, light_magenta, bold, green, light_green, yellow,
light_yellow, white, gray

